| `templates/nmstate-br-ex.yml.j2` | NMState YAML: br-ex bridge, ens5 as port, ens6 secondary |
| `templates/99-nmstate-br-ex.yaml.j2` | MachineConfig wrapping the NMState file (base64 encoded) |
